549
00:23:23,830 --> 00:23:24,560
Is that true?

550
00:23:25,710 --> 00:23:27,240
But I didn't agree either.

551
00:23:27,270 --> 00:23:28,710
What kind of talk is that?

552
00:23:28,890 --> 00:23:30,910
Xie Tiancheng, what were you thinking?

553
00:23:30,910 --> 00:23:32,100
Are your brains damaged from all the drinking?

554
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:33,870
It's his last year of senior high.

555
00:23:33,870 --> 00:23:35,240
You can't wait for such a short time?

556
00:23:35,240 --> 00:23:36,450
You even said we were both useless,

557
00:23:36,450 --> 00:23:37,660
and we'd need our son to provide for us.

558
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:38,910
What were you thinking?

559
00:23:38,910 --> 00:23:40,290
What kind of talk is that?

560
00:23:40,290 --> 00:23:41,470
What are you talking about?

561
00:23:41,470 --> 00:23:42,230
This... You...

562
00:23:42,230 --> 00:23:42,950
Let me beat him first.

563
00:23:42,950 --> 00:23:43,630
Don't beat him.

564
00:23:43,630 --> 00:23:44,950
